msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_MENDERW\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This prototype aether crew drone repairs at an acceptable speed while boosting crew and weakening enemies.\n"
"    \n"
"-50 HP, 1.5x repair speed, 2x movement speed\n"
"-Friendly crew in the same room as the mender will be immune to suffocation damage.\n"
"-Enemy crew in the same room as the mender will be stripped of their suffocation immunity and have their resistance set to 2x damage taken.\n"
"-Inflicts a 10s stun when destroyed"

