#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5244
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_BEAM\"]/title"
msgstr "Salt Beam"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5245
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_BEAM\"]/short"
msgstr "Salt B."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5246
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_BEAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A one-of-a-kind weapon forged by the legendary, fallen Salt Empire. It fires"
" a highly compressed beam of gaseous salt that inflicts minor damage to the "
"ship, and poisons crew for 50 seconds, dealing 5 hp/s. The beam kills Slugs "
"instantly."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5340
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_SNIPER\"]/title"
msgstr "Salt Sniper"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5341
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_SNIPER\"]/short"
msgstr "Salt Snip."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5342
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_SNIPER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This legendary weapon fires a single projectile that penetrates all shields,"
" deals 3 damage to hull and 6 to systems, and poisons crew for 10 seconds, "
"dealing 10 hp/s. The cannon kills Slugs and destroys drones instantly."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5456
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_ION\"]/title"
msgstr "Salt Ion"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5457
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_ION\"]/short"
msgstr "Salt Ion"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5460
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SALT_ION\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This peculiar weapon of the lost Salt Empire fires a single projectile, "
"piercing all shields, dealing 3 ion damage, locking down the target room, "
"and inflicting a light poison for 20 seconds that deals 2 hp/s. Slugs and "
"drones take 6 hp/s instead."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5582
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SLIMER_BOMB\"]/title"
msgstr "Sticky Bomb"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5583
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SLIMER_BOMB\"]/short"
msgstr "Sticky B."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5585
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SLIMER_BOMB\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Self-teleporting explosive of Slimer's grand design. Deals minor system "
"damage, prevents repair, and makes crew move at 0.1x speed for 10 seconds. "
"Can target your own ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5631
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PHYS_BEAM\"]/title"
msgstr "'Physure' Beam"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5632
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PHYS_BEAM\"]/short"
msgstr "'Physure'"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5633
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PHYS_BEAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A simple, yet powerful ion beam weapon, forged with a modicum of Phys' "
"eternal suffering. Stuns all enemy drones if the beam hits drone control "
"directly."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5635
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PHYS_BEAM\"]/descriptionOverride"
msgstr ""
"A simple, yet powerful ion beam weapon, forged with a modicum of Phys' eternal suffering. Stuns all enemy drones if the beam hits drone control directly.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tStats:\n"
"\t\tRequired Power: 3\n"
"\t\tCharge Time: 25 seconds\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tBeam Length: 100\n"
"\t\tBeam Speed: 5\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tTotal Crew Damage: 60\n"
"\t\tIon Damage: 2\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tStuns All Enemy Drones for: 5 Seconds\n"
"\n"
"\t\tDefault Price: 100~   -   Selling Price: 50~"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5651
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PHYS_BEAM\"]/tooltipOverride"
msgstr ""
"Required Power: 3\n"
"\t\tCharge Time: 25 seconds\n"
"\n"
"\t\tBeam Length: 100\n"
"\t\tBeam Speed: 5\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tTotal Crew Damage: 60\n"
"\t\tIon Damage: 2\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tStuns All Enemy Drones for: 5 Seconds"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5690
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ALEENOR_BIO_PIERCE\"]/title"
msgstr "Aleenor's Pierce Irradiation Laser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5691
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ALEENOR_BIO_PIERCE\"]/short"
msgstr "Rad Pierce"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5693
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ALEENOR_BIO_PIERCE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A precise bio piercing weapon designed by Aleenor. It will deal heavy damage"
" to any crew unlucky enough to be struck by it while also removing their "
"suffocation immunity and causing them to take +1x suffocation damage for 10 "
"seconds. Doesn't disrupt cloaking when fired."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5757
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_VIN_MISSILE\"]/title"
msgstr "'Prometheus' Missiles"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5758
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_VIN_MISSILE\"]/short"
msgstr "'Prometheus'"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5759
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_VIN_MISSILE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Vin's pet project. Likely the hottest gun in the Multiverse, it fires a powerful missile that inflict low system damage, but always start fires and temporarily burns enemies over time, dealing 10 damage per second for 10 seconds which scales with the crew hit's fire damage taken. Negative fire resistance will cause crew hit to heal instead.\n"
"\n"
"\tNegative fire resistance will cause crew hit to heal instead."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5763
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_VIN_MISSILE\"]/descriptionOverride"
msgstr ""
"Vin's pet project. Likely the hottest gun in the Multiverse, it fires a powerful missile that inflict low system damage, but always start fires and temporarily burns enemies over time, dealing 10 damage per second for 10 seconds which scales with the crew hit's fire damage taken. Negative fire resistance will cause crew hit to heal instead.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tStats:\n"
"\t\tRequired Power: 3\n"
"\t\tCharge Time: 16 seconds\n"
"\t\tMissile Consumption: 1\n"
"\t\tAccuracy Bonus: 10%\n"
"\n"
"\t\tShots Per Charge: 1\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tBase Hull Damage: 2\n"
"\t\tTotal System Damage: 1\n"
"\t\tTotal Crew Damage: 60\n"
"\t\tShield Piercing: 10\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tFire Chance 100%\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tDamages crew hit for: 10 hp/s for 10 seconds which scales with the crew's fire damage taken (negative values will heal the crew instead).\n"
"\n"
"\t\tDefault Price: 160~   -   Selling Price: 80~"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5784
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_VIN_MISSILE\"]/tooltipOverride"
msgstr ""
"Required Power: 3\n"
"\t\tCharge Time: 16 seconds\n"
"\t\tMissile Consumption: 1\n"
"\t\tAccuracy Bonus: 10%\n"
"\n"
"\t\tShots Per Charge: 1\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tBase Hull Damage: 2\n"
"\t\tTotal System Damage: 1\n"
"\t\tTotal Crew Damage: 60\n"
"\t\tShield Piercing: 10\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tFire Chance 100%\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tDamages crew hit for: 10 hp/s for 10 seconds which scales with the crew's fire damage taken (negative values will heal the crew instead)."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5847
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"fr_ghostly_drone\"]/title"
msgstr "Ghostly Drone"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5848
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"fr_ghostly_drone\"]/short"
msgstr "Ghostly Drone"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5849
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"fr_ghostly_drone\"]/desc"
msgstr "YOU SHOULD NEVER SEE THIS."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5853
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"fr_ghostly_drone\"]/powerList/power"
msgstr "DRONE"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5859
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_GHOSTLY_DRONE_BOARDER\"]/title"
msgstr "Spectral Battle Drone [Boarding]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5860
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_GHOSTLY_DRONE_BOARDER\"]/short"
msgstr "Spectral [ATK]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5861
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_GHOSTLY_DRONE_BOARDER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"[CURRENT MODE: Boarding] Cleo's pride and joy. A powerful boarding drone that can teleport around the enemy ship.\n"
"    \n"
"-150 HP, 2x movement speed\n"
"-1.5x crew damage, can teleport within the ship it's in."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5875
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_GHOSTLY_DRONE_DEFEND\"]/title"
msgstr "Spectral Battle Drone [Anti-Pers]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5876
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_GHOSTLY_DRONE_DEFEND\"]/short"
msgstr "Spectral [DEF]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5877
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_GHOSTLY_DRONE_DEFEND\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"[CURRENT MODE: Anti-Personnel] Cleo's pride and joy. A powerful boarding drone that can teleport around the enemy ship.\n"
"    \n"
"-150 HP, 2x movement speed\n"
"-1.5x crew damage, can teleport within the ship its in."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5890
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ZULU_PIKE\"]/title"
msgstr "Holy Pike"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5891
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ZULU_PIKE\"]/short"
msgstr "Holy Pike"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5893
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ZULU_PIKE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Forged in the depths of Tartarus by Zulu's ancestors, this high-quality beam"
" weapon is quite overtuned for its energy consumption."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5921
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_PLASMA_ENEMY\"]/title"
msgstr "Necromantic Cannon (enemy)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5922
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_PLASMA_ENEMY\"]/short"
msgstr "Necro. C."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5924
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_PLASMA_ENEMY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"G's favorite self-constructed weapon. It fires a massive spray of shots that"
" do nothing but pierce all shields and inflict a powerful erosion effect."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5980
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_PLASMA\"]/title"
msgstr "Necromantic Cannon"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5981
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_PLASMA\"]/short"
msgstr "☠ Plasma"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:5983
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_PLASMA\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"G's favorite self-constructed weapon. It fires a massive spray of shots that"
" do nothing but pierce all shields and inflict a powerful erosion effect."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6039
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_LASER\"]/title"
msgstr "Necromantic Harbinger"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6040
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_LASER\"]/short"
msgstr "☠ Harbinger"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6042
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_LASER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A strange laser forged by G, imbued with the mysterious power of necromancy."
" It fires a burst of powerful projectiles that each apply a strong corrosion"
" effect and crack the hull."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6095
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_COMBAT_MISSILE\"]/title"
msgstr "Necromantic Missile Drone"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6096
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_COMBAT_MISSILE\"]/short"
msgstr "☠ Missile"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6097
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_COMBAT_MISSILE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A modified Obelisk missile drone fueled by black magic. It deals no hull or "
"system damage, but moves extremely fast, spreads a strong corrosion effect, "
"and deals damage to non-ghost crew."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6114
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_DRONE_MISSILES\"]/title"
msgstr "Ancient Missiles"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6115
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_DRONE_MISSILES\"]/short"
msgstr "A. Missile"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6116
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NECROMANTIC_DRONE_MISSILES\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"An ancient Missile Launcher, far outdating any launcher you've ever seen."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6243
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SPECTER_BEAM_1\"]/title"
msgstr "'Duskblade' Beam MK I"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6244
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SPECTER_BEAM_1\"]/short"
msgstr "'Duskblade' I"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6245
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SPECTER_BEAM_1\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This horrifying weapon made from the most concentrated ectoplasm in all of "
"Tartarus has the ability to pierce most shield layers while also summoning "
"spirits to aid you in combat. This ghosts will stick around if they live "
"through the battle and can be recovered if you have a teleporter."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6279
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FROSTWALL_CRYSTAL_ION\"]/title"
msgstr "Frostwall's Crystal Phaser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6280
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FROSTWALL_CRYSTAL_ION\"]/short"
msgstr "Crystal Phase"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6282
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FROSTWALL_CRYSTAL_ION\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A strange mix of a crystal and a phaser. This powerful weapon can keep rooms"
" locked almost permanently."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6329
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SPAWN_ENEMY\"]/title"
msgstr "Lesser Eldritch Spawn"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6330
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SPAWN_ENEMY\"]/short"
msgstr "L. Spawn"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6331
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SPAWN_ENEMY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A mysterious creature birthed from the mind of an eldritch power. Their power has been greatly drained however.\n"
"    \n"
"-Takes 20% damage from comabt. Cannot be stunned or mind controlled. Destroying Drone Control will repel it.\n"
"-3x repair speed. 0.5x movement speed. 1.5x crew damage and sabotage speed.\n"
"-Technopaths can't copy its eldritch systems."

