#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6505
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_POK_MORPH_DRONE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"[CURRENT MODE: MORPH] A cursed contraption which shoots from a variety of an endless supply of living morphs at the enemy. Can swap between all 3 morph types like an AMP drone, with the drone requiring more power and becoming slower the better the morphs are. \n"
"\t\t\n"
"Morphs pierce all shields, use no crew slots, can't be cloned and live for 20 seconds."

