"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_CHARROR_DRONE\"]/title"
msgstr "'Debugger' Pinpoint Drone"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6864
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_CHARROR_DRONE\"]/short"
msgstr "'Debugger'"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6865
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_CHARROR_DRONE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A beam drone, heavily modified by Charror. The energies of Tartarus flow "
"through it, allowing it to hack any system room hit by it, though it cannot "
"deal normal system damage. It cannot disrupt systems impeded by a Hacking "
"drone."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6880
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_CHARROR_DRONE_PINPOINT\"]/title"
msgstr "Debug Drone Beam"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6899
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LEO_FLAK\"]/title"
msgstr "Leo's Battery Flak Gun"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6900
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LEO_FLAK\"]/short"
msgstr "Battery Flak"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6901
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LEO_FLAK\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This strange flak gun has an internal battery system which can not only "
"fully power itself, but also provides 2 power to whichever weapon is "
"directly to the right of it in the weapon list."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6945
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SEARAK_ENERGY\"]/title"
msgstr "Searak's Irradiation Energy Cannon"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6946
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SEARAK_ENERGY\"]/short"
msgstr "Rad Energy"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6948
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SEARAK_ENERGY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Searak's custom energy cannon which has been tuned to be able to deal heavy "
"damage to crew in the room without sacrificing the usual benefits of energy "
"weapons. Heavily weakens crew hit."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6994
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LEGION_DRONE_BATTLE_BOARDER\"]/title"
msgstr "Legionnaire Pyrotechnic Battledrone [Boarding]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6995
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LEGION_DRONE_BATTLE_BOARDER\"]/short"
msgstr "Legion B. [ATK]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:6996
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LEGION_DRONE_BATTLE_BOARDER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"[CURRENT MODE: Boarding] A nightmare machine made by the Legion. Built out of a secret aether alloy and fuled by pure liquid aether, this machine can spew flames that are hot enough to melt solid aether chunks in seconds.\n"
"    \n"
"-175 Max Health, 0.45x movement speed, immune to hazards.\n"
"-Attacks extremely fast in combat, but only deals 0.5x damage.\n"
"-Starts fires in the room after attacking for 5 seconds.\n"
"-Deals double damage to crew with exposed flesh.\n"
"-Explodes on death, damaging any system and crew in the room and starting fires."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:7013
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LEGION_DRONE_BATTLE_DEFEND\"]/title"
msgstr "Legionnaire Pyrotechnic Battledrone [Anti-Pers]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:7014
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LEGION_DRONE_BATTLE_DEFEND\"]/short"
msgstr "Legion B. [DEF]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:7015
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//droneBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LEGION_DRONE_BATTLE_DEFEND\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"[CURRENT MODE: Anti-Personnel] A nightmare machine made by the Legion. Built out of a secret aether alloy and fuled by pure liquid aether, this machine can spew flames that are hot enough to melt solid aether chunks in seconds.\n"
"    \n"
"-175 Max Health, 0.45x movement speed, immune to hazards.\n"
"-Attacks extremely fast in combat, but only deals 0.5x damage.\n"
"-Starts fires in the room after attacking for 5 seconds.\n"
"-Deals double damage to crew with exposed flesh.\n"
"-Explodes on death, damaging any system and crew in the room and starting fires."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:7036
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"fr_technolegion_battle\"]/powerList/power[1]"
msgstr "Currently mimicking: Legionnaire Pyrotechnic Battledrone"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:7046
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_WATCHER_PINPOINT\"]/title"
msgstr "'Iah' Pinpoint"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:7047
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_WATCHER_PINPOINT\"]/short"
msgstr "'Iah'"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:7048
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_WATCHER_PINPOINT\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"You can barely look at this beam weapon without feeling dizzy. It fires a "
"concentrated beam of static that pierces shields, wreaks havoc on systems, "
"and turns the mind of the crew hit blank, preventing them from acting for 10"
" seconds."

