"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PRINCE_CANNON\"]/short"
msgstr "Hell-Breach"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:7506
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PRINCE_CANNON\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Opens a portal to Hell in the room hit. Any crew that passes through it will"
" have their soul energy syphoned to power up the portal, summoning a demonic"
" spawn in 5 seconds after entering the room. The portal will close in 20 "
"seconds, but the demon can be recovered after the fight."

