"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_TRIRIAC_ABDUCTOR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A weapon beyond all understanding. It can only fire once per fight, but it "
"pierces all shields, teleports the target crew to your ship, and permanently"
" breaks their mind, making them yours."

