msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_BEAM_VISION\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Fires an absolutely overwhelming stream of chaotic power. Deals heavy crew "
"damage while inflicting Absolute Madness, preventing them from taking any "
"action or using their abilities."

