msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ROYAL_ANCIENT_ARTILLERY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful ancient Beam weapon that sweeps across entire ships, decimating "
"their hull and systems. This elite version always ignites fires instead of "
"breaches, and deals more damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:8301
