msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_GOLDEN_ANCIENT_MINELAUNCHER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"An extremely heavy, hard-hitting minelauncher made out of solid gold. Obviously, that also makes it extremely valuable.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tAt empty beacons provides 2 fleet delay for 30 scrap. Doesn't impact your notoriety."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:8345
