"drones shoot 10 times before vanishing."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:14288
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ARTILLERY_REVENANT_CLEO_B\"]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"Deploy 2 temporary Auto Loot laser combat drones that will attack the enemy "
"ship when fired. The drones shoot 10 times before vanishing."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:14324
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ARTILLERY_REVENANT_CLEO_C\"]/title"
msgstr "Cleo's Atom Drone Artillery"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:14325
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ARTILLERY_REVENANT_CLEO_C\"]/short"
msgstr "Cleo A. Art."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:14326
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"FR_ARTILLERY_REVENANT_CLEO_C\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"[Base cooldown: 2.5] This unique artillery deploys a single Royal Atom drone"
