"A powerful piece of technology that bolsters the power of your beam and pinpoint weapons and artilleries. \n"
"\t\t\n"
"\tThey deal 2 extra damage of all of the types they normally deal, with crew damage being raised by 30 instead.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tThe extra damage won't appear in the weapon's stats."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19123
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_BEAM_STORE\"]/title"
msgstr "Beam Merchant Hotline"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19124
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_BEAM_STORE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Allows you to access a store that, every time it is summoned, offers 3 random beams or pinpoint weapons and 3 random beam or pinpoint drones, each at a 45% discount. \n"
"\t\t\n"
"\tAny non-artillery beam can appear in this store."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19134
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FREE_FORM_TELEPORTERS\"]/title"
msgstr "Free-Form Teleporters"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19135
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FREE_FORM_TELEPORTERS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Your crew and drones can teleport between empty rooms while inside your "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19143
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SPHERAX_MAKER\"]/title"
msgstr "Spherax Constructor"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19144
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SPHERAX_MAKER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This highly advanced machine can forge new Spherax at empty beacons. The "
"process is fairly expensive."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19152
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_ION_ARMOR_NEUTRALIZER\"]/title"
msgstr "Ion Armor Neutralizer"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19153
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_ION_ARMOR_NEUTRALIZER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This unique piece of Commonwealth technology infects the enemy ship and "
"strips it clean of ion resistances. Not even Salt ships are immune to this "
"effect."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19161
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_AUTO_HUNTER_GEAR\"]/title"
msgstr "Auto Hunter Gear"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19162
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_AUTO_HUNTER_GEAR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This unique augment allows its user to track down Continuity probes and "
"fight them for their gear and scrap. It also doubles the damage your weapons"
" do against automated ships."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19170
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_COLLECTORS_SHIELD\"]/title"
msgstr "Collector's Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19171
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_COLLECTORS_SHIELD\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A strangely resistant shield powered by several massive Aether batteries "
"with an integrity of 12 hitpoints. This unique variant of the shield also "
"regenerates to full integrity every 30 seconds."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19179
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_AETHER_PHEROMONES\"]/title"
msgstr "Aether Pheromones"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19180
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_AETHER_PHEROMONES\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A concoction of aether dust and heavily synthesized Free Mantis pheromones. \n"
"\t\t\n"
"\tWhile your Life Support system is powered, makes all friendly crew give +1 power (stacks with existing effects) and makes them deal damage on death, the latter scales with system level, starting with 30 up to 120 at level 4. The death effect stacks with existing effects as well."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19190
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NARRATIVE_SHIELD\"]/title"
msgstr "Narrator's Presence"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19191
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NARRATIVE_SHIELD\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This supershield is the closest thing that I, Narrator Sylvan, can have to a physical presence. \n"
"\t\t\n"
"\tNot only do I have an integrity of 15 hit points, but I will also allow you to select between any and all blue options in any event! With my guidance, you will never be unprepared again."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19201
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OVERCHARGED_AETHER_SHIELDS\"]/title"
msgstr "Overcharged Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19202
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OVERCHARGED_AETHER_SHIELDS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This aether supershield is powered by one of the biggest aether batteries ever designed by the Obelisks.\n"
"\n"
"\tHas an integrity of 12 hitpoints at the cost of slowing your shield recharge rate by 20%."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19212
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_REFUGE_SHIELDS\"]/title"
msgstr "Refuge's Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19213
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_REFUGE_SHIELDS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"By overloading all batteries in the ship and setting them in series with each other, this ship's super shield is capable of absorbing the ion from non-bomb ion attacks and redirecting it by releasing it as a copy of the enemy projectile.\n"
"\n"
"\tHas an integrity of 10 hitpoints and is immune to ion damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19223
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PROTOTYPE_SHIELDS\"]/title"
msgstr "Prototype Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19224
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PROTOTYPE_SHIELDS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The most cutting edge shield in the Obelisk's arsenal, straight out of the designing phase and into the battlefield.\n"
"\n"
"\tThis shield will constantly stun any enemy combat drones for as long as the supershield is up.\n"
"\n"
"\tHas an integrity of 14 hitpoints."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19236
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_EXTERMINATORS_SHIELDS\"]/title"
msgstr "Exterminator's Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19237
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_EXTERMINATORS_SHIELDS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The aether shield that protects the Exterminator is powered by the biggest Aether battery to ever be designed by the Obelisks.\n"
"\n"
"\tIt has an integrity of 18 hitpoints and boosts standard shield charge rate by 25%."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19247
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LICHS_SHIELDS\"]/title"
msgstr "Lich's Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19248
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LICHS_SHIELDS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The accursed shield sacrifices guaranteed protection for a single, extremely resistant layer.\n"
"\n"
"\tIt has an integrity of 1 hitpoint but a 85% chance to resist all types of damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19258
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_QUEENS_AEGIS\"]/title"
msgstr "Queen's Aegis"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19259
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_QUEENS_AEGIS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The personal energy shield of the queen's cruiser. This powerful piece of technology was developed in secrecy and only a handful of Obelisks even know of its existence.\n"
"\n"
"\tCan block all attempts to limit your systems or reactor for as long as the super shield is up.\n"
"\n"
"\tIt has an integrity of 20 hitpoints."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19278
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_COMBAT_OMNI_JAMMER\"]/title"
msgstr "System Omni-Jammer"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19279
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_COMBAT_OMNI_JAMMER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful electronic warfare unit constructed using technology from faraway realities. Can be activated at the start of the combat to limit any enemy system by 2 bars for the entire fight.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t[Uses 2 power. The Emergency Generator can be used to remove the power consumption, at the cost of only limiting the target system by 1 bar.]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19288
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_COMBAT_HACKED_OMNI_JAMMER\"]/title"
msgstr "Hacked Omni-Jammer"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19289
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_COMBAT_HACKED_OMNI_JAMMER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"An absurdly powerful system disruption unit which uses Nexus technology. Can"
" mimic the effect every non-omni system jammer, alongside their blue "
"options."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19302
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_TIIIKAKA_CARD_USED\"]/title"
msgstr "Tiiikaka card used"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19303
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_TIIIKAKA_CARD_USED\"]/desc"
msgstr "now in augment form."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19310
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_1\"]/title"
msgstr "Gun Parts Half"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19311
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_1\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Parts of an unknown weapon. Currently non-functional without the parts from "
"the other package."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19318
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_2\"]/title"
msgstr "Gun Parts Complete"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19319
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"All the parts needed to assemble an unkown weapon. Currently non-functional "
"until you can get someone to assemble them for you."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19332
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_DELOADER\"]/title"
msgstr "De-loader"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19333
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_WEAPON_DELOADER\"]/desc"
msgstr "The fire rate of your Weapons and Artillery is made slower by 10%."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19342
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SHIELD_DECHARGE\"]/title"
msgstr "Shield Charge Leaker"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19343
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SHIELD_DECHARGE\"]/desc"
msgstr "Slows the ship's shield recharge rate by 17%."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19352
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FTL_JAMMER\"]/title"
msgstr "FTL Jammer"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19353
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FTL_JAMMER\"]/desc"
msgstr "The ship's FTL Drive powers up 30% slower."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19362
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PILOT_ONLY_MANNING\"]/title"
msgstr "Pilot Only Manning"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19363
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_PILOT_ONLY_MANNING\"]/desc"
msgstr "Makes pilot the only system being mannged."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19372
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_NOBLE_SURGE\"]/title"
msgstr "Noble Surge"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19373
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_NOBLE_SURGE\"]/desc"
msgstr "Enables the obelsik surge if the ship starts with this."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19382
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_ROYAL_SURGE\"]/title"
msgstr "Royal Surge"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19383
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_ROYAL_SURGE\"]/desc"
msgstr "Enables the obelsik surge if the ship starts with this."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19392
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_COMMONWEALTH_SURGE\"]/title"
msgstr "Commonwealth Surge"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19393
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_COMMONWEALTH_SURGE\"]/desc"
msgstr "Enables the obelsik surge if the ship starts with this."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19402
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_WITHER_SURGE\"]/title"
msgstr "Wither Surge"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19403
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_WITHER_SURGE\"]/desc"
msgstr "Enables the obelsik surge if the ship starts with this."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19412
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_G_SURGE\"]/title"
msgstr "G Surge"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19413
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_G_SURGE\"]/desc"
msgstr "Enables the obelsik surge if the ship starts with this."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19422
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_Y_SURGE\"]/title"
msgstr "Y Surge"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19423
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_Y_SURGE\"]/desc"
msgstr "Enables the obelsik surge if the ship starts with this."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19432
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ANTIAUG_ION_ARMOR\"]/title"
msgstr "Anti-Ion-Armor"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19433
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ANTIAUG_ION_ARMOR\"]/desc"
msgstr "You lose the ability to resist ion."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19442
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ION_ARMOR_NEUTRALIZER\"]/title"
msgstr "Anti ion defense nullifier"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19443
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ION_ARMOR_NEUTRALIZER\"]/desc"
msgstr "Negates all ion defenses."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19451
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_TRIRIAC_SHIELD_B\"]/title"
msgstr "Tririac Shield B"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19452
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_TRIRIAC_SHIELD_B\"]/desc"
msgstr "Funny Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19460
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_TRIRIAC_SHIELD_C\"]/title"
msgstr "Tririac Shield C"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19461
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_TRIRIAC_SHIELD_C\"]/desc"
msgstr "Funny Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19469
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ANTIAUG_AUG_EVERYTHING_PIERCE\"]/title"
msgstr "Anti-Omni-Pierce"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19470
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ANTIAUG_AUG_EVERYTHING_PIERCE\"]/desc"
msgstr "All Weapons Lose 1 Lose Piercing"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19479
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ANTIAUG_AUG_EVERYTHING_PIERCE_DRONE\"]/title"
msgstr "Anti-Omni-Pierce Drones"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19480
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"ANTIAUG_AUG_EVERYTHING_PIERCE_DRONE\"]/desc"
msgstr "All Drones Lose 1 Lose Piercing"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19489
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SUSTAIN_PROTOCOL\"]/title"
msgstr "Sustain Protocol"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19490
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SUSTAIN_PROTOCOL\"]/desc"
msgstr "Crew is immune while the Medbay is powered."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19498
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FULL_AUTO\"]/title"
msgstr "Full Auto Ship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19499
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FULL_AUTO\"]/desc"
msgstr "This is a fully Auto ship, any new crew will be instantly killed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19507
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_DAMAGED_WEAPONS\"]/title"
msgstr "Damaged Weapon System"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19508
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_DAMAGED_WEAPONS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship's weapons took a heavy beating, they will take 50% longer to "
"charge."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19516
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_UNSLOTED_GHOSTS\"]/title"
msgstr "Unslotted Ghosts"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19517
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_UNSLOTED_GHOSTS\"]/desc"
msgstr "Revenants don't use crew slots anymore."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19525
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HER_VISION\"]/title"
msgstr "Her Vision"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19526
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HER_VISION\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Breaches are automatically repaired, fires are automatically put out, the "
"ship will only be destroyed if its hull loses its last 3 points of health in"
" one attack."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19534
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FORGOTTEN_WALLACE\"]/title"
msgstr "Forgotten Wallace's Store"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19535
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FORGOTTEN_WALLACE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Grants access to the forgotten store which sells all Forgotten Races things."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19543
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FORGOTTEN_AENWITHER_CREWSER\"]/title"
msgstr "Forgotten crew selection"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19544
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_FORGOTTEN_AENWITHER_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr "lets you get the fr uniques in the storage menu."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19552
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NEXUS_ARM_ELECTROMAGNETIC_DEBUFF\"]/title"
msgstr "Electromagnetic Debuff"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19553
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_NEXUS_ARM_ELECTROMAGNETIC_DEBUFF\"]/desc"
msgstr "Enemy's accuracy is lowered by 10%."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19561
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SIREN_TELEPORT\"]/title"
msgstr "Dissection Room"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19562
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_SIREN_TELEPORT\"]/desc"
msgstr "Crews in this room take damage at a rate of 15 hp/s."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19570
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_CABAL_ROOMS\"]/title"
msgstr "Cabal Rooms"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19571
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_CABAL_ROOMS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Your weapon and medbay rooms can't be breached, set on fire and takes no "
"hull damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19586
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SALT_INSTALLED\"]/title"
msgstr "Salt"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19587
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SALT_INSTALLED\"]/desc"
msgstr "Salt upgrade installed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19593
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SALT_PRO_SLUG_SALT\"]/title"
msgstr "Pro-Slug Salt"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19594
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SALT_PRO_SLUG_SALT\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Salt's area damage stops dealing damage to Slugs of all kinds and instead "
"heals them but in exchange it now deals double the damage to every other "
"race. Obyns have their ability's damage changed instead to deal double the "
"damage to enemies and allied while also healing Slugs instead of damaging "
"them."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19600
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SALT_OATH_OF_PEACE\"]/title"
msgstr "Oath of Peace"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19601
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SALT_OATH_OF_PEACE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Salts can't fight directly but instead have their sabotage damage set at 2x "
"and move at 0.5x speed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19607
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SALT_HEALING_CRYTALS\"]/title"
msgstr "Healing Crystals"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19608
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SALT_HEALING_CRYTALS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Salts have their room wide dot now heals them for as much as it damages enemies while Obyns have their ability heal themselves and nearby allies for 6 hp/s but lose the ability to deal damage with said ability.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\tSalts and Obyns now take 100% more damage from all sources."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19617
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_OSMIAN_INSTALLED\"]/title"
msgstr "Osmian"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19618
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_OSMIAN_INSTALLED\"]/desc"
msgstr "Osmian upgrade installed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19624
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_OSMIAN_LIGHT_HELPERS\"]/title"
msgstr "Light Helpers"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19625
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_OSMIAN_LIGHT_HELPERS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Osmians gain 20% health, repair speed, combat and sabotage damage if they "
"have a hologram in the same room as them."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19631
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_OSMIAN_ONE_BODY\"]/title"
msgstr "One Body"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19632
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_OSMIAN_ONE_BODY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Osmians don't generate holograms anymore, instead they gain the base "
"hologram stats for 30 seconds (25% damage taken resistance, immune to mind "
"control, phases through doors, can't burn or suffocate and gives 1 power to "
"the system they are in)."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19638
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_OSMIAN_SOULFUL_LIGHT\"]/title"
msgstr "Soulful Light"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19639
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_OSMIAN_SOULFUL_LIGHT\"]/desc"
msgstr "Osmian's holograms last forever but have 50% lower stats."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19646
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_ELEMAN_INSTALLED\"]/title"
msgstr "Eleman"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19647
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_ELEMAN_INSTALLED\"]/desc"
msgstr "Eleman upgrade installed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19653
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_ELEMAN_UNSTABILITY\"]/title"
msgstr "Elemental Instability"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19654
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_ELEMAN_UNSTABILITY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Snowmen automatically create breaches and Lavamen automatically start fires "
"while in the enemy ship at the cost of 50% of their crew damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19660
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_ELEMAN_ABSORPTION\"]/title"
msgstr "Temperature Absorption"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19661
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_ELEMAN_ABSORPTION\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Snowman will now heal from suffocation damage and Lavamen from fire damage. "
"Their health is halved however."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19667
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_ELEMAN_MAINTENANCE\"]/title"
msgstr "High Maintenance Bodies"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19668
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_ELEMAN_MAINTENANCE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Snowman and Lavaman will now use 2 crew space each but will gain 50% health,"
" 20% damage and 25% movement and repair speed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19675
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPHERAX_INSTALLED\"]/title"
msgstr "Spherax"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19676
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPHERAX_INSTALLED\"]/desc"
msgstr "Spherax upgrade installed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19682
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPHERAX_REFOCUSED\"]/title"
msgstr "Refocused Energies"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19683
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPHERAX_REFOCUSED\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Spheraxes lose the ability to teleport, but gain 100 extra health, +15% "
"damage and +25% sabotage speed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19689
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPHERAX_BEHAVIOUR\"]/title"
msgstr "Non-Aggressive Behavior"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19690
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPHERAX_BEHAVIOUR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Not having any Spherax on the enemy ship will give your Spherax 2x repair "
"speed. Spheraxes on the enemy ship deal 0.5x damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19696
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPHERAX_ELETRONIC\"]/title"
msgstr "Electronic Dominance"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19697
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPHERAX_ELETRONIC\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Spherax lose the ability to sabotage but will automatically hack doors in "
"the enemy ship and unhack them in yours."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19705
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPECTER_INSTALLED\"]/title"
msgstr "Specter"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19706
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPECTER_INSTALLED\"]/desc"
msgstr "Specter upgrade installed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19712
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPECTER_FLAWLESS_ASCENSION\"]/title"
msgstr "Flawless Ascension"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19713
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPECTER_FLAWLESS_ASCENSION\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Your Specters take twice as long to charge their abilities but their abilities become boosted in unique ways.\n"
"\t\tSlimer: \n"
"\t\t- DEVOUR: Removes the system damage and allows it to be used in the enemy ship.\n"
"\t\t- EAT: Now deals 75 damage to enemy crew and heals Slimer for 35 for each enemy crew in the room.\n"
"\t\tPhys: Ion damage is raised to 8 and the stun now only affects enemies.\n"
"\t\tAleenor: Raises crew damage to 100 damage and system damage to 4 damage.\n"
"\t\tVin:\n"
"\t\t- BOOST: Removes the self damage.\n"
"\t\t- FUSION: Vin's fire healing will be doubled for 10 seconds after activating the ability.\n"
"\t\tCleo: The drones also gain double damage for the duration.\n"
"\t\tZulu: Removes the movement speed, sabotage and damage penalties during the effect.\n"
"\t\tG: Also spawns 3 undead specters for the duration.\n"
"\t\tFrostwall: Removes the self damage and causes frozen crew to take full damage for the duration.\n"
"\t\tDeathbloom: Dobules the duration of the spores and lowers enemy's speed while affected by the spores by 10%.\n"
"\t\tPok: Their morph ability's cooldown is cut to 10 seconds in all forms.\n"
"\t\tCharror: Their ability now affects all crew types and only applies to enemies.\n"
"\t\tLeo: The increased damage taken now applies to enemies in the room instead.\n"
"\t\tSearak: Removes the post explosion stun.\n"
"\t\tAugustus: Now only costs 1 scrap to fully heal him.\n"
"\t\tSally: The hatchling and adult abilities now only have a 1 second cooldown, while the weaver form ability's affects all ships.\n"
"\t\tPrince: Breaches and starts a fire in the room as well.\n"
"\t\tTririac: Tririac becomes immune to stun during the effect."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19741
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPECTER_TAILORED_SPECIALIZATION\"]/title"
msgstr "Tailored Specialization"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19742
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPECTER_TAILORED_SPECIALIZATION\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Your Specters' strengths and well as their weaknesses are vastly improved.\n"
"\t\tSlimer: Reduces his active ability cooldowns by 50% - Halves his crew damage.\n"
"\t\tPhys: Provides double her base power - Can't sabotage.\n"
"\t\tAleenor: Doubles her damage - Can't repair.\n"
"\t\tVin: Doubles his health - Halves his speed.\n"
"\t\tCleo: Gains a 1.3x bonus to health, speed, repair and damage - Cannot fight enemy drones directly. \n"
"\t\tZulu: Doubles his sabotage damage - Halves his crew damage.\n"
"\t\tG: Doubles the healing gained from hazards - Raises her active ability cooldowns by 50%.\n"
"\t\tFrostwall: Doubles his ranged damage - Halves his hp.\n"
"\t\tDeathbloom: Sets her o2 production to 2.0 (old was 0.1) - Halves her heal speed. \n"
"\t\tPok: They move 50% faster and reduces their active ability cooldowns by 50% - They use 2 crew slots.\n"
"\t\tCharror: Doubles their repair speed - Halves their crew damage.\n"
"\t\tLeo: Doubles their power drain - Doubles their stun time.\n"
"\t\tSearak: Halves his damage taken - Halves his sabotage damage.\n"
"\t\tAugustus: Adds a 1.2x multipler to his sabotage, damage and health - Halves his movement speed.\n"
"\t\tSally: Constantly heals for 15 hp/s - Halves health.\n"
"\t\tPrince: Doubles movement speed - Halves repair speed.\n"
"\t\tTririac: Doubles the damage mind controled crew do in the same room as them - They are stunned 10 times longer."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19766
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPECTER_SPECTRAL_EXISTENCE\"]/title"
msgstr "Spectral Existence"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19767
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_SPECTER_SPECTRAL_EXISTENCE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Specters don't use up any crew slots. Generic Specters will be prioritized "
"first in crew loss events above *any* other crew."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19773
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_REVENANT_TRUE_UNDEATH\"]/title"
msgstr "True Undeath"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19774
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_LAB_REVENANT_TRUE_UNDEATH\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Revenants can't be cloned or heal through normal means but will instead be "
"revived on jump."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19786
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_HUMAN_TEAMWORK\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Teamwork Neurons"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19787
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_HUMAN_TEAMWORK\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Humans gain 15% repair speed and combat damage for each human in the room minus themselves.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19796
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_HUMAN_DIVERSE\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Diversification"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19797
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_HUMAN_DIVERSE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Humans gain a 12% buff in movement speed, combat damage, repair speed, and health.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19806
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_SLUG_BUFF\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Neural Redirection"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19807
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_SLUG_BUFF\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Slugs lose the ability to sense crew on the other ship, but gain a 25% boost to combat, sabotage, and repair speed.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19816
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_SHELL_TELEPATHY\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Evolutionary Rebranching"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19817
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_SHELL_TELEPATHY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Shells inherit the telepathic abilities of Slugs.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19826
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_MANTIS_MELEE\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Selective Killing"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19827
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_MANTIS_MELEE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Mantis do an extra 60% damage in melee combat, but lose 50% of their ranged damage.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19836
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_ROCK_SPEED\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Crumbling Exterior"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19837
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_ROCK_SPEED\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Rockmen move 75% faster, but lose 12% Max Health.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19846
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_LANIUS_METAL\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Selective Metalworking"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19847
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_LANIUS_METAL\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Lanius repair and sabotage 50% faster, but do 30% less crew damage.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19856
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_CRYSTAL_SABOTAGE\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Hardened Crystals"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19857
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_CRYSTAL_SABOTAGE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Crystals gain 75% sabotage damage, but lose 50% of their move speed.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19866
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_ORCHID_THORNS\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Thorns"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19867
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_ORCHID_THORNS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Orchids do x1.3 ranged damage.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19876
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_ENGI_EFFICIENCY\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Nanite Efficiency"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19877
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_ENGI_EFFICIENCY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Engi crew gain 15% repair speed.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19886
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_LEECH_POWER\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] High Voltage"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19887
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_LEECH_POWER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Leeches are stunned for 50% longer and take 33% more fire and asphyxiation damage but provide power on the player ship.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19896
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_ZOLTAN_SHIELD\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Hard-Light Shielding"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19897
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_ZOLTAN_SHIELD\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Zoltans shield other crew in the room, making them take 33% damage, but cannot directly fight other crew themselves.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19906
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_GHOST_HEALTH\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Denser Molecules"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19907
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_GHOST_HEALTH\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Ghosts gain 20 extra health.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19916
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_SPIDER_PREDATOR\"]/title"
msgstr "[L] Predatory Instincts"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19917
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_LAB_SPIDER_PREDATOR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Spiders can't repair at all or man systems, but gain 50% combat damage and movement speed.\n"
"\t\n"
"[L] - As an external lab upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. It cannot be converted into an actual lab upgrade, but will not consume your primary slot. Does not stack with itself."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19932
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_BASE\"]/title"
msgstr "Hektar Modular Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19933
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_BASE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful energy shield created by the one and only Billvan. It has an integrity of 10 hitpoints, and can be modified with any Hektar module to apply a powerful secondary effect.\n"
"\tModule Effects:\n"
"\tCooldown: Boosts shield recharge rate by 200%.\n"
"\tAnti-Bio: Makes your ship an Auto-ship while slotted.\n"
"\tStun: Your crew become immune to stun. Enemies are stunned for triple the normal duration, and they will be stunned automatically every 5 seconds while in your ship.\n"
"\tPierce: Enemy weapons and drones pierce 7 fewer shield layers.\n"
"\tHullbuster: Provides a 50% chance to negate incoming hull damage.\n"
"\tLockdown: Your non-beam weapons apply lockdown. All of your weapons pierce an additional shield layer.\n"
"\tFire: Your systems and crew don't take fire damage.\n"
"\tAccuracy: Your weapons have 30% more accuracy.\n"
"\tPower: The energy shield's integrity is increased to 20 layers, but your normal shields will have their recharge rate reduced by 50%."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19951
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_BIO\"]/title"
msgstr "Hektar Modular Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19952
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_BIO\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful energy shield created by the one and only Billvan. It has an integrity of 10 hitpoints, and can be modified with any Hektar module to apply a powerful secondary effect.\n"
"\t----CURRENTLY INSTALLED MODULE----\n"
"\tAnti-Bio: Makes your ship an Auto-ship while slotted."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19963
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_COOLDOWN\"]/title"
msgstr "Hektar Modular Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19964
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_COOLDOWN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful energy shield created by the one and only Billvan. It has an integrity of 10 hitpoints, and can be modified with any Hektar module to apply a powerful secondary effect.\n"
"\t----CURRENTLY INSTALLED MODULE----\n"
"\tCooldown: Boosts shield recharge rate by 200%."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19976
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_LOCKDOWN\"]/title"
msgstr "Hektar Modular Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19977
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_LOCKDOWN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful energy shield created by the one and only Billvan. It has an integrity of 10 hitpoints, and can be modified with any Hektar module to apply a powerful secondary effect.\n"
"\t----CURRENTLY INSTALLED MODULE----\n"
"\tLockdown: Your non-beam weapons apply lockdown. All of your weapons pierce an additional shield layer."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19989
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_PIERCE\"]/title"
msgstr "Hektar Modular Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:19990
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_PIERCE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful energy shield created by the one and only Billvan. It has an integrity of 10 hitpoints, and can be modified with any Hektar module to apply a powerful secondary effect.\n"
"\t----CURRENTLY INSTALLED MODULE----\n"
"\tPierce: Enemy weapons and drones pierce 7 fewer shield layers."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:20001
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_STUN\"]/title"
msgstr "Hektar Modular Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:20002
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_STUN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful energy shield created by the one and only Billvan. It has an integrity of 10 hitpoints, and can be modified with any Hektar module to apply a powerful secondary effect.\n"
"\t----CURRENTLY INSTALLED MODULE----\n"
"\tStun: Your crew become immune to stun. Enemies are stunned for triple the normal duration, and they will be stunned automatically every 5 seconds while in your ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:20013
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_ACCURACY\"]/title"
msgstr "Hektar Modular Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:20014
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_ACCURACY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful energy shield created by the one and only Billvan. It has an integrity of 10 hitpoints, and can be modified with any Hektar module to apply a powerful secondary effect.\n"
"\t----CURRENTLY INSTALLED MODULE----\n"
