#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:20026
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_FIRE\"]/title"
msgstr "Hektar Modular Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:20027
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_FIRE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A powerful energy shield created by the one and only Billvan. It has an integrity of 10 hitpoints, and can be modified with any Hektar module to apply a powerful secondary effect.\n"
"\t----CURRENTLY INSTALLED MODULE----\n"
"\tFire: Your systems and crew don't take fire damage."

