msgstr "Blessing of The Ion"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21539
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_FR_COMMONWEALTH_EQUIPMENT\"]/desc"
msgstr "Your ship gains 50% ion resistance."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21546
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_FR_SALT_CREW\"]/title"
msgstr "Boon of the Forgotten."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21547
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_FR_SALT_CREW\"]/desc"
msgstr "Your Salts become immune to suffocation and stuns."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21560
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP\"]/class"
msgstr "Obelisk Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21561
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP\"]/name"
msgstr "The Destroyer"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21562
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Save the long extinct race of aliens by destroying their oppressor's "
"strongest vessel."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21563
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This is the original base for the Exterminator, a proof of concept that was "
"never used. It may lack the power of its royal variant, but it is still a "
"force to be reckoned with."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21639
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Commonwealth's Obelisk Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21640
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Saviour"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21641
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21642
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After the alliance between the Federation and the Commonwealths was formed, the two super powers worked together to create a ship that could stand up to the might of the Royals.\n"
"This ship is the result of that program."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21724
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Prototype Obelisk Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21725
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Obliterator"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21726
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21727
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Fresh off the production line, this monstrous cruiser has received minimal "
"testing before being approved for battle, as is customary for the work of "
"the Devisers."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21803
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP\"]/class"
msgstr "Royal Obelisk Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21804
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP\"]/name"
msgstr "The Exterminator"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21805
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Destroy the Exterminator and get the Commonwealth ending using any layout of"
" the Obelisk Flagship line."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21806
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After Queen Y's defeat, the Federation managed to gather enough information about the Exterminator's original design to replicate it.\n"
"Luckily, a few Royals survived the fight and \"willingly\" offered to join the cause."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21883
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Lich's Obelisk Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21884
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Soul Taker"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21885
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21886
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Rejected by the remaining Royals and unwelcomed in the Refuge for obvious "
"reasons, the only thing G can do is spread her misery across the multiverse "
"using a modified Exterminator model."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21961
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Absolute Obelisk Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21962
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The All-Ending"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21963
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:21964
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ELITE_OBELISK_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship is the outcome of a near-impossible scenario: The alliance of "
"different Ys across multiple realities. The outcome? A vessel capable of "
"destroying all that come across it."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22038
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN\"]/class"
msgstr "Deserter Sylvan Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22039
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN\"]/name"
msgstr "The Deserter"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22040
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Befriend the long extinct race of aliens and then help the ex-travelling "
"merchant to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22041
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This Sylvan gave up his life of traveling the multiverse for a humbler one "
"with the Commonwealth. Now, forces outside his control have forced him to "
"activate his MV drive once more."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22117
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Deserter Sylvan Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22118
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The T-800"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22119
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22120
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"While on the run from Prime for his blunder, the Collector came across "
"Cylvan who allowed him to stay in the Commonwealth refuge if he agreed to "
"hunt down any C.E.L. probes that got in their way."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22195
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Deserter Sylvan Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22196
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Shunned"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22197
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22198
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_DESERTER_SYLVAN_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After being kicked out from the Nexus, the friendly free Mantis Sylvan found"
" a new home among the Commonwealths, who accept him for who he is."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22271
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX\"]/class"
msgstr "Precursor Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22272
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX\"]/name"
msgstr "The Psi"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22273
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Explore the ruins of a forgotten race in the center of the Multiverse to "
"unlock this cruiser."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22274
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser belongs to the Spherax, a race that existed before all of known"
" history. None of the original weapons survive, but the Spherax themselves "
"have been successfully reconstructed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22347
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Precursor Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22348
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Nova Spera"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22349
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22350
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The Spherax properly integrated into the Federation following a long "
"bureaucratic process. This ship was constructed out of gratitude."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22428
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Precursor Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22429
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Perfection"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22430
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22431
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SPHERAX_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship managed to return its Spherax constructor to working order. Its "
"absurd layout makes the ship inhospitable to almost everyone else."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22505
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED\"]/class"
msgstr "Perfected Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22506
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED\"]/name"
msgstr "Absolute Convergence"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22507
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Unlock all ships from the Obelisk line, Commonwealth line, Alt Aenwithe line"
" and Aenwithe's crewser to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22508
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship was constructed as a perfect union of each Obelisk caste. Its "
"shield and artillery combine the power of each into one overwhelming force."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22579
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Perfected Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22580
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Melting Pot"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22581
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Unlock all Augmented ships from both base Multiverse and Forgotten Races, "
"including Crewsers."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22582
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship stands above all other Lanius vessels as the ultimate Augmented "
"cruiser, bearing a hull composition that takes the best from the collective "
"efforts of all types of Augmented."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22654
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Perfected Ship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22655
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Moment"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22656
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Unlock both Guardian ships from Forgotten Races."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22657
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PERFECTED_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This vessel came to be as a perfect union of all of the Obelisks' work on "
"artificial intelligence. The Cognitives aboard can retain a modicum of self-"
"control even when liberated."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22736
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BROKEN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/class"
msgstr "Fallen Obelisk Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22737
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BROKEN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/name"
msgstr "The Former Glory"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22738
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BROKEN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Manage to hack into the broken cruiser deep in Obelisk territory to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22739
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BROKEN_COMMONWEALTH\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This vessel was once staffed by a third subset of the Obelisks that died off"
" long ago during the interspecies war. All that remains is a few strange "
"guns, a Cognitive, and the broken corpse of one of its creators. "
"Unfortunately, its once great forge was too badly damaged by the passage of "
"time."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22818
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BROKEN_COMMONWEALTH_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Daisy's Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22819
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BROKEN_COMMONWEALTH_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Bellrennis' Revenge"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22820
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BROKEN_COMMONWEALTH_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a once dead Obelisk about a certain artifact to unlock"
" this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22821
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BROKEN_COMMONWEALTH_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Now fully fixed and restored to her personal colors, Daisy's personal "
"cruiser is ready to explore the frontiers of space and kick the asses of any"
" Exterminators it comes across!"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22897
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH\"]/class"
msgstr "Commonwealth Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22898
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH\"]/name"
msgstr "The Jarvis"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22899
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult a certain Obelisk corpse about a certain artifact to unlock this "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22900
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser was offered to the Federation as a gift after the integration "
"into their ranks. With Commonwealth technology on their side, alongside the "
"power to make more, the Federation is ready to make waves like never before."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22978
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Commonwealth Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22979
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Grey Goo"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22980
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:22981
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship boasts a unique twist on the usual Obelisk artillery, constructing"
" swarms of drones instead of firing a payload."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23054
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Commonwealth Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23055
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Electrification"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23056
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23057
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship's unique properties strengthen all of its non-beam weapons, "
"increasing their ability to ionize ships."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23131
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED\"]/class"
msgstr "Enhanced Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23132
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED\"]/name"
msgstr "The Forbidden Snack"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23133
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Save the last of a kind from being killed to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23134
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This breed of Augmented are very uncommon, having feasted on a specific type"
" of Obelisk technology. The ship starts with weak systems, but its crew are "
"more than willing to tear the ship apart to rectify that."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23208
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Enhanced Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23209
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Cloak And Dagger"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23210
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23211
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship focuses on shredding systems before the enemy can even lift a "
"finger, saving you hull for upgrades."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23285
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Enhanced Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23286
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Black-Scholes"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23287
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23288
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ENHANCED_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship sacrifices conventional defense for a powerful boarding party and "
"a hull repair drone, allowing it to get even more value out of tearing "
"itself apart."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23363
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN\"]/class"
msgstr "Commonwealth Guardian Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23364
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN\"]/name"
msgstr "Warfare Protocol"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23365
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Stop the Auto rampage in a secret and long-forgotten realm to unlock this "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23366
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This marvel of automated technology boasts an advanced internal repair "
"network, but lacks the ability to obtain better doors or a medical system."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23425
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Commonwealth Guardian Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23426
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Elevated Permission"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23427
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23428
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The friendship between this ship's Cognitive and onboard AI is so strong "
"that the former entrusted most of the ship's functions to the latter. The "
"Cognitive sealed off most of the ship, but the automatic repairs make that "
"less of an issue."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23504
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Commonwealth Guardian Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23505
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Multithread"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23506
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23507
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COMMONWEALTH_GUARDIAN_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship is used as a refuge for two types of robotic crew, freed from "
"their creators' shackles and ready to carve their own path."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23583
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER\"]/class"
msgstr "Alt-Aenwithe Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23584
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Pride of Aenwithe"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23585
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain Obelisk engineer about a certain artifact to"
" unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23586
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The personal cruiser of Aenwithe. With a lot of unexpected free time on his "
"hands, he decided to go out and explore the Multiverse - and it seems there "
"are a lot of other Aenwithes out there to keep him company."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23658
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Alt-Aenwithe Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23659
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Opulent Dream"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23660
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23661
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Aenwithe was finally able to afford his dream ship after saving up funds for"
" centuries - an Obelisk cruiser made of solid gold!"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23734
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Alt-Aenwithe Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23735
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "One Of Us"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23736
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23737
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_ALT_WITHER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"An insane sequence of events led Aenwithe to become a traveling merchant "
"amongst the Sylvans and their Nexus. This cruiser, and its signature weapon,"
" is the result of his fitting facelift."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23810
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN\"]/class"
msgstr "Prototype Guardian Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23811
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN\"]/name"
msgstr "The Factorio"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23812
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Clear out the broken aether ship in the Dynasty capital to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23813
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The lead research ship of the \"Deviser\" branch of the Obelisk empire, led "
"by Aenwithe. It boasts a unique set of tools that allows it to forge "
"experimental Obelisk weaponry on the go."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23888
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Prototype Guardian Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23889
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Sadism"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23890
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23891
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship focuses on spreading utter chaos with its powerful companion "
"drone."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23967
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Prototype Guardian Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23968
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Oxymoron"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23969
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:23970
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHER_GUARDIAN_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"An extremely unlikely chain of events led this Obelisk Auto-ship to be "
"captured and refitted by... the Dynasty?"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24046
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED\"]/class"
msgstr "Withered Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24047
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED\"]/name"
msgstr "The Hit And Run"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24048
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Bring a particular type of Lanius to a certain trio of observers."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24049
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Piloted by the Withered and constructed from mysterious blueprints, this "
"ship fights fast and hard, using its hull plating to absorb scratch damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24122
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Withered Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24123
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Slow Rider"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24124
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24125
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship starts with a huge gun that can shred through ships, but requires "
"its crew's assistance to handle shielding."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24199
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Withered Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24200
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Reflection"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24201
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24202
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WITHERED_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship relies on its ablative armor to damage the enemy ship's hull. "
"Thankfully, its boarding crew are more than adept at rendering its target "
"harmless first."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24278
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/class"
msgstr "Federation Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24279
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/name"
msgstr "The Heron"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24280
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Stop the Rebellion's plans in the Contested Warzone to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24281
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The end result of the \"Project Retribution\", The Heron can take on other "
"flagships with its mix of standard artilleries and a upgraded version of the"
" Federation's signature beam artillery."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24359
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Federation Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24360
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Peacock"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24361
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24362
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A scrapped early prototype for The Heron that went all in on beam "
"technology. While it was meant to be destroyed, an anonymous member of the "
"project stole the ship and sold it to a beam aficionado and their crew."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24438
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Militia Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24439
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Owl"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24440
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24441
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After the revolutionary success of Project Retribution, modified versions of"
" The Heron were distributed to all Federation allied factions, one of those "
"being the Militia."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24521
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP\"]/class"
msgstr "Unity Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24522
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP\"]/name"
msgstr "The Seriema"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24523
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Win with all 3 layouts of the Federation Flagship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24524
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The apex of the Federation's attempts to build a flagship-class ship. It has"
" its own unique beam artillery made specifically for it and some of the "
"strongest technology from the Federation's members. It does, however, come "
"at the cost of its hull."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24600
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Totality Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24601
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Teratornithidae"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24602
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24603
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Built in utmost secrecy, unauthorized discussion of this vessel's existence "
"is grounds for immediate court martial. With artilleries powered by the "
"weapons of fallen renegades, this ship can break anyone that opposes its "
"goals."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24678
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Stolen Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24679
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Haemophilia"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24680
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24681
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_UNITY_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After fully retrofitting the Federation flagship with Rebel technology, "
"Victor was awarded their own personalized model of it as a thank you gift "
"from Vance himself. Why they are now fighting for the Federation is a "
"mystery, however."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24756
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/class"
msgstr "Coalition Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24757
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/name"
msgstr "The Mellifera"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24758
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Stop the Coalition's plans in the Contested Warzone to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24759
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The most secretive and powerful class of ships ever deployed by the "
"Coalition, this flagship-class ship can raze the defenses of sectors all by "
"itself, if fought without reinforcements."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24837
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Anti-Coalition Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24838
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Ammoplanidae"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24839
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24840
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After finishing the paperwork that made the \"Anti-Coalition\" an official "
"faction, its leaders realized they needed a big ship to showcase their "
"might. And what better choice than to steal a flagship from the Coalition "
"itself?"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24921
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Lost Sun Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24922
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Lampyridae"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24923
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:24924
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This stolen flagship was the biggest win the Lost Suns ever had against the "
"Coalition. Retrofitting their strongest ship to serve their cause will "
"surely change the tides of war in their favor."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25002
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP\"]/class"
msgstr "R.U.E.S. Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25003
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP\"]/name"
msgstr "The Mandarinia"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25004
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Win with all 3 layouts of the Coalition Flagship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25005
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This horrifying ship once threatened a sector filled with both Unity and MFK"
" Ace ships, all armed to the teeth. The fact the outcome of that incursion "
"wasn't set in stone at the outset speaks volumes about the sheer power of "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25083
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/class"
msgstr "E.C.H.O. Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25084
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Liphistius"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25085
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25086
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This flagship was commissioned and built by two individuals who both wanted "
"to stay anonymous. It houses some of the multiverse's most exotic crew. A "
"shame it comes with next to no power or systems to start with."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25163
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/class"
msgstr "R.U.E.S. Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25164
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Cerambycidae"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25165
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25166
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_RUES_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Out of infinite universes out there, there is an infinite amount of "
"realities where Rockmore defected from the Coalition, willingly or "
"otherwise. This unfortunately isn't your reality, but he's willing to help "
"you at the very least."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25239
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Jon's Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25240
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "Skylab"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25241
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain lead technician about a certain artifact to "
"unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25242
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Jon's personal cruiser, one of the very few Wentworth Innovation ships to be"
" equipped with a multiverse drive. With his brand new Drone Booster 2.0 in "
"hand and finally unshackled from his responsibilities, he's ready to take "
"destiny by the reins."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25320
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Jon's Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25321
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Elytra"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25322
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25323
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After being fired from his job for being caught helping Federation ships, "
"Jon was approached by the Syndicate and offered a position in their ranks. "
"Lacking many other options, he agreed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25401
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Genius' Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25402
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Death Egg"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25403
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25404
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_JON_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"What happens when the two greatest minds of the Rebellion meet? This ship is"
" the result of that question. No longer will the name of Doctor Eggman be "
"besmirched by drunken rebels, the doctor is finally in and ready to make his"
" mark."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25481
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Corsair Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25482
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "Corsair's Wail"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25483
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain unaffiliated pirate corsair about a certain "
"artifact to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25484
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"In another time, Purple Beard managed to steal Vance 1's prized flagship "
"before leaving Universe 1. With such a powerful ship, he was forced to "
"command it after becoming the de facto leader of the unaffiliated pirates."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25559
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Angelic Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25560
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Vitasphere"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25561
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25562
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After losing his crew to an MFK Ace ambush, Purple Beard was left with no "
"choice but to join the Syndicate for his own protection. Luckily, Vael "
"offered him an honorary position between his Angels of Death in exchange for"
" his unquestioned loyalty."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25637
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Pandora Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25638
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Mystery Box"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25639
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25640
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_PURPLE_BEARD_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"No one knows how the legendary pirate came in contact with the beings in "
"charge of the pandora's boxes. All that's known is that on that day, a pact "
"was sealed which bound him into their service for as long as he lived."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25717
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Mantis Royal Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25718
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Regina Aurea"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25719
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain Mantis Queen about a certain artifact to "
"unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25720
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The one and only personal cruiser of Queen Leikonpliiinakra. It is equipped "
"with a special blend of pheromones that allows Mantis to... not completely "
"suck at repairing things?"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25791
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Mantis Royal Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25792
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Honeymoon"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25793
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25794
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After marrying the Queen, Kazaaakplethkilik decided to refit her old cruiser"
" into a ship the both of them could be proud of. She doesn't like the pirate"
" paint."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25866
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Mantis Royal Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25867
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Rule Of Two"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25868
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25869
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_MANTIS_QUEEN_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A ship which symbolizes newfound unity between the Hive and the Free Mantis,"
" commanded by both of their leaders and flooded with a mix of both of their "
"pheromones."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25946
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Archive Inc. Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25947
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "S.E.L.M.A."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25948
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain Archive drone about a certain artifact to "
"unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:25949
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After learning how dangerous a Rebel victory would be to their collections, "
"Archive Inc. decided to join the fight with a spacefaring vessel. "
"Unfortunately, the old Gana model of crew drone was all they could muster to"
" command the ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26025
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Archive Inc. Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26026
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Nimda"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26027
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26028
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After being taken over by A55, this ship was recolored to resemble the "
"pirate king's old cruiser. He did keep the Gana drone and internal archives "
"intact, thankfully."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26105
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Archive Inc. Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26106
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "I.R.I.S."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26107
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26108
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GANA_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After securing the contents of a wrecked, cube-shaped ship, Archive Inc. "
"decided to use some of the technology found inside of it to upgrade their "
"existing cruiser model."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26183
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN\"]/class"
msgstr "Snowman Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26184
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN\"]/name"
msgstr "The Vostok"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26185
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a Snowman about a certain artifact OR Win the game "
"with the C layout to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26186
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A ship inhabited by living snow people, ready to throw hands with anyone who"
" makes fun of their literal carrot noses."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26259
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Lavaman Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26260
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Kilauea"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26261
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a Lavaman about a certain artifact OR Reach sector 5 "
"with the A layout."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26262
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A ship made to sustain the rare cousins of the Snowmen: the Lavamen. The "
"inside of this ship is lined with spare ignition chemicals, allowing them to"
" revive themselves when killed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26337
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Elemental Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26338
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Maxwell"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26339
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26340
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SNOWMAN_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After a long political back-and-forth, the two known types of elemental "
"decided to create a ship that can support both of their needs."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26412
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER\"]/class"
msgstr "Tester Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26413
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Tester"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26414
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Use the Federation Database to ditch your old ship to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26415
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship used to be a testbed for prototype technologies. Recent "
"refurbishments have allowed this classic ship to spring into combat once "
"more."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26490
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Arcadia Prototype"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26491
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "AM"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26492
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26493
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"An extremely advanced Auto-ship developed by Arcadia. Although it boasts an "
"extremely powerful drone constructor artillery, it cannot support crew at "
"all or wield weapons."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26551
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Tester Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26552
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Martyr's Vengeance"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26553
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26554
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_TESTER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"On the way to defeating the Flagship, a team of Renegades towed this "
"derelict ship back to port. It roams the Multiverse with its own widely "
"varied compliment now, as a memorial to those lost in the Multiversal War."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26634
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP\"]/class"
msgstr "Salt Battleship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26635
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP\"]/name"
msgstr "The Revival"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26636
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Help a certain bounty hunter rediscover a lost population OR unlock all four"
" Sodium ships to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26637
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This vessel may be the last of its kind, a memory of a fallen empire. It is "
"equipped with a powerful beam which allows for variability in its combat "
"strategy."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26712
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Salt Battleship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26713
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Violent Reaction"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26714
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This rare Salt vessel threw everything into offense, crippling its ability "
"to defend itself in exchange for gaining a powerful precision weapon."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26715
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26791
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Salt Battleship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26792
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Electrolysis"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26793
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26794
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SALT_BATTLESHIP_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Salt vessels are not even slowed by ion weaponry. This vessel takes "
"advantage of that by fielding overcharged ion weaponry, using it to support "
"Salt boarders."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26868
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE\"]/class"
msgstr "Osmian Prototype"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26869
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE\"]/name"
msgstr "The Maw"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26870
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Help a lost colony fight their oppressors OR unlock all Osmian Cruisers to "
"unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26871
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A secret project, stolen by the Osmians during the war against the Ministry."
" It boasts a dangerous artillery weapon, powered by a stabilized black hole."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26946
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Osmian Prototype"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26947
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Dancing Lights"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26948
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:26949
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Once a design concept that never made it into production, this variant was "
"given a second chance at life. It can swarm enemy ships with hard-light "
"foes, using its artillery to conjure them forth."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27024
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Osmian Prototype"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27025
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The TLC"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27026
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27027
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_OSMIAN_PROTOTYPE_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"An attempt to redesign the Osmian prototype as a medical vessel. The healing"
" energy of its vortex has proven to be a highly successful tool for both "
"warfare and war relief."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27093
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Cyra's Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27094
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "Provecta Cohortis"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27095
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of the first MFK about a certain artifact to unlock this "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27096
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Cyra's personal cruiser has everything anybody could need to train even the "
"weakest of humans into full-fledged MFK Aces just like herself. It helps "
"that she's the best one to teach new recruits, too."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27169
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "MFK Training Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27170
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Baby's First Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27171
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27172
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After a long training regimen, Cyra has given Leah and Jerry their final "
"task - destroy a Multiverse Flagship without her guidance. She gave them the"
" right tools for the job, but forgot to upgrade the ship to match."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27246
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Collaborative Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27247
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Gemini"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27248
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27249
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYRA_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"At the behest of Admiral Vance, Cyra has undertaken her next mission with a "
"complementary crew of Wentworth Technicians."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27322
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Michael's Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27323
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Funkalicious"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27324
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain mascot about a certain artifact to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27325
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser is the official promotional cruiser for the new hit show Sammy "
"the Spider. Flowers and Sunshine also equipped it to be a gunship, likely "
"because of the Multiverse War tearing up everything in sight."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27400
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Promotional Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27401
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Spider Dance"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27402
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27403
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser is the result of an outreach by Flowers and Sunshine to a new "
"demographic: actual giant alien spiders. Thankfully, they do seem interested"
" in both money and more spiders."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27478
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Reunion Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27479
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Farewell Tour"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27480
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27481
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SAMMY_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Aboard this cruiser, Sammy the Spider and Ellie the Equinoid reunite for one"
" final episode."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27557
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Boss' Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27558
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Shining Pearl"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27559
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain crime lord about a certain artifact to "
"unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27560
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The one and only personal cruiser of Goziodeon, retrofitted for his personal"
" needs after he finally defeated his lifelong nemesis: the Spook Chasers."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27632
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Family's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27633
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Addam"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27634
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27635
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This is what you get when multiple Goziodeons form a Multiversal pact, "
"running their criminal operations together. Unfortunately, the ship was not "
"designed with non-Ghosts in mind."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27706
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Henchmens' Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27707
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Power Vacuum"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27708
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27709
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_GOZER_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser belongs to a group of Haunts from a universe where Goziodeon "
"met his end at the hands of the Spook Chasers. Now, they continue to plot "
"against their old foe, carefully planning their next strike."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27784
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Captain's Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27785
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Glory Days"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27786
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain blue humanoid about a certain artifact to "
"unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27787
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship is a true anomaly. It appears to come from a distant cluster where"
" the Multiversal War never happened, and yet one which is far more cruel."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27860
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "AI Avatar Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27861
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Cortana"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27862
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27863
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship comes prepackaged with a machine that allows it to generate "
"endless artificial intelligence allies. They may be fragile, but that is no "
"issue."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27939
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Captain's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27940
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Non Transibis"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27941
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:27942
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_STEFAN_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A secret Rebel prototype ship that was stolen by several Rebel turncoats "
"before it could ever be deployed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28017
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Venomous Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28018
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Funnelweb"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28019
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain mutated spider about a certain artifact to "
"unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28020
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After ridding herself of all control by the Brood, Charlotte has stolen an "
"abandoned vessel and, with the help of the one pirate that helped her escape"
" captivity, now only seeks the destruction of the Brood."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28090
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Predatory Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28091
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "War And Peace"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28092
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28093
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After decades of infighting, the two known G.A.S. broods finally forged a "
"peace treaty. Now, they have constructed a vessel capable of accommodating "
"both their queens."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28164
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Flaming Spider Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28165
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Matchstick"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28166
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28167
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VENOMOUS_SPIDER_QUEEN_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship was retrofitted by a psychopathic captain with an affinity for "
"burning spiders alive. The spiders promptly proceeded to evolve and "
"overthrow the vessel's old owner."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28242
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Cyberpony Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28243
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Cyberpunked"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28244
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain cybernetic pony about a certain artifact to "
"unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28245
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This Separatist Engi appears to genuinely believe that they are an Equinoid."
" Of course, they're also a fan of Ellie the Equinoid, which certainly hasn't"
" helped matters."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28321
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Cyberpony Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28322
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Rarity"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28323
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28324
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The Cyberpony has finally found a companion who will accept them for who "
"they strive to be. They also don't know how uncommon Crystalline Equinoids "
"such as their friend are."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28399
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Cyberpony Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28400
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Reboot"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28401
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28402
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CYBERPONY_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"In this far-fetched timeline, Flowers and Sunshine hired the Cyberpony as "
"their new mascot, and their ship was refitted accordingly."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28472
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Leah's Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28473
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Beam of Justice"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28474
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain longtime nemesis about a certain artifact to"
" unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28475
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After being formally accepted into the ranks of the Federation, Leah has "
"retrofitted this Rebel vessel into what she believes is the perfect cruiser."
" It boasts advanced beam technology, sourced from her father's absurd "
"wealth."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28551
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Beam Mastery Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28552
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The M.O.A.B."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28553
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28554
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Leah has surrounded herself with a number of highly trained soldiers to "
"staff her ship. A few old friends in the Rebellion also helped her overhaul "
"her beam-enhancing technology."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28629
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Beam Mastery Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28630
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Death Star"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28631
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28632
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEAH_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"In this universe, Leah managed to climb the ranks of the Rebellion to the "
"point where she was allowed to join the Legion. When she eventually defected"
" to the Feds, she couldn't help but smuggle her old cruiser away."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28705
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "Elite Beyatch Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28706
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Deity of Beams"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28707
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Spare a certain longtime nemesis in the center of the Multiverse to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28708
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Syleah was exiled from the Nexus Point for calling Sylvan Prime a "
"\"beyatch\" one too many times. So, she threw her lot in with the Federation"
" and became one of the most powerful Renegades to ever exist."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28782
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Billvan's Crewser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28783
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Accolade"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28784
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Stand down without fighting a Hektar cashier in the center of the Multiverse"
" to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28785
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser is a homage and a tribute from Billvan to his brother, and an "
"attempt to thrust light into the future of the Multiverse while he's at it."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28860
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Narrative Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28861
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Plot Armor"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28862
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Acquire the Bucket in center of all things to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28863
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_SYLEAH_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"While life in the Nexus was comfortable, it always lacked the true experience of exploring the multiverse yourself. Onward, Renegade! To destiny!\n"
"\n"
"\tBy playing this ship you forgo the rights to have a balanced experience."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28942
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO\"]/class"
msgstr "C.E.L. Auto-Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28943
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO\"]/name"
msgstr "Oculi Praesidium"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28944
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Betray the long extinct race of aliens and then kill the ex-travelling "
"merchant to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:28945
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"An automated vessel employed by one of the most powerful organizations in "
"the Multiverse. It is capable of installing unique internal upgrades as a "
"result of its powerful construction."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29021
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO_2\"]/class"
msgstr "C.E.L. Auto-Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29022
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Prohibitum Locum"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29023
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29024
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser was stolen by the mysterious Sirens as part of a grand plan. It is equipped with abduction tools in order to aid its study of all life in the Multiverse.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tThis ship also comes with a internal version of the Nexus schematics."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29100
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO_3\"]/class"
msgstr "C.E.L. Auto-Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29101
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO_3\"]/name"
msgstr "V"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29102
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29103
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CEL_AUTO_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"An operation from the Hacker Clan managed to capture and reprogram this Auto-ship from the C.E.L.. They have repurposed some of the ship's technology to make the ultimate system jammer.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tThis ship also comes with a internal version of the Nexus schematics."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29180
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER\"]/class"
msgstr "MFK Flagship Ace"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29181
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Atonement"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29182
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Consult the advice of a certain admiral about a certain artifact to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29183
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Vance Prime's personal flagship. It now flies alongside the Federation, yet "
"still bears its MFK stripes with pride."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29243
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Jerry's Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29244
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Teatime For Two"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29245
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29246
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A special request from Jerry to his uncle, in an attempt to create an "
"environment where both of them could repair their familial bond. However, "
"multiple systems had to be heavily downsized in order to divert enough power"
" to fuel the artilleries."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29318
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Admirals' Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29319
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Hope Rekindled"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29320
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29321
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_VANCE_PRIME_CREWSER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Realizing the error of his ways, Vance partnered with Tully to forge a "
"Flagship that would be perfect for the both of them. Although it is "
"extremely offensively capable, it suffers from a general lack of protection."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29395
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REAL\"]/class"
msgstr "R.E.A.L. Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29396
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REAL\"]/name"
msgstr "Order and Chaos"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29397
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REAL\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Defeat Her."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29398
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REAL\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The Reality Enhancement and Annihilation League was forged after Sylvan "
"Prime and Her decided to work together, an alliance once thought completely "
"impossible."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29462
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REAL_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Observers' Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29463
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REAL_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Fortuna"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29464
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REAL_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29465
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REAL_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This enigmatic cruiser was once under the employ of the C.E.L. before the "
"Observers stole it in order to flee from a tight spot. They now blaze their "
"own path for once, finally having a hand in the Multiverse they were "
"previously just forced to watch."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29537
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER\"]/class"
msgstr "Slimer's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29538
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Confection"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29539
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Put to rest the soul of a gluttonous Slug to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29540
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This vessel was originally a simple pleasure liner before Slimer took it and"
" retrofitted it to satisfy his endless hunger."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29612
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Slimer's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29613
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Endless Feast"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29614
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29615
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After tasting the flesh of some of the rarest crew in the multiverse, Slimer"
" has made it his life goal to hunt and consume as many of them as he can. "
"And to make sure his crew follows him to the end, they are also inflicted by"
" the same unending hunger."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29689
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Slimer's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29690
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Oligarch's Dream"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29691
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29692
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SLIMER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After Slimer's return to power by beating both Slocknog and Nights at the "
"Crown Theft Festival, he recognized their power and capabilities, something "
"the slugs in his time lacked. And so, he offered them a chance to all rule "
"as one, a chance they begrudgingly took."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29767
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS\"]/class"
msgstr "Phys' Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29768
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS\"]/name"
msgstr "The Disruptor"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29769
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Put to rest the soul of a broken Shell to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29770
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A vessel wielded by Phys in her quest to stop the everlasting suffering "
"coursing through her being. It is filled with ionized gases that pose a true"
" threat to boarders."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29842
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Phys' Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29843
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Shell-Shocked"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29844
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29845
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Phys' unique genetic structure makes her extremely potent in the support "
"role for boarding strategies. To support her powers, her crew were outfitted"
" with powerful suits that make stunning enemies easy and which provide stun "
"resistance."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29920
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Phys' Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29921
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Tetrachromacy"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29922
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29923
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_PHYS_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After successfully raiding Phys' ship, the Geniocracy decided to use it as "
"the launching point of their new experiment, a perfected mixture of all the "
"Shell gases."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29996
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR\"]/class"
msgstr "Aleenor's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29997
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR\"]/name"
msgstr "The Supra Mortem"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29998
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Put to rest the soul of a prideful Bishop to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:29999
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Aleenor's personal craft, forged within the depths of Tartarus after her "
"death. It is equipped with a one-of-a-kind blend of pheromones."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30072
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Aleenor's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30073
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Invisible Strike"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30074
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30075
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship's formidable boarding team relies on Aleenor's personal brand of "
"pheromones to board the enemy ship. As such, oxygen is critical."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30151
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Aleenor's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30152
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Plated Claws"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30153
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30154
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ALEENOR_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Aleenor's contributions to the Mantis Hive didn't go unnoticed by the Rock "
"Theocracy. After a long negotiation session, they commissioned a unique "
"layout for the fallen Mantis, staffed by their best soldiers and plated with"
" their thickest armor."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30229
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN\"]/class"
msgstr "Vin's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30230
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN\"]/name"
msgstr "The Molten Omen"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30231
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Put to rest the soul of a vengeful Paladin to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30232
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A cruiser belonging to Vin, an ever-melting Paladin. Its interior is "
"legitimately flooded with lava, rendering it utterly inhospitable for anyone"
" who isn't a Rockman or Ghost themselves."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30305
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Vin's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30306
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Death Valley"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30307
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30308
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The fire and lava in this ship burn with a strange green hue, possibly "
"because of the influence of all the vagabonds in the ship. It has the same "
"effect as its normal counterpart, though it looks more haunting."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30383
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Vin's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30384
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Prophet's Flame"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30385
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30386
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_VIN_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"While out in search of a traitor to the inquisition, Vin came across the "
"True Prophet's vessel right before the final ceremony. Taking matters into "
"his own hands, Vin intended to kill the mad man, however he ended up being "
"made the leader of the cult instead."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30464
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO\"]/class"
msgstr "Cleo's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30465
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO\"]/name"
msgstr "The Agoraphobia"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30466
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Put to rest the soul of a paranoid Ace to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30467
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"There is not a single set of quarters aboard this ship other than Cleo's. "
"Instead, the ship's drone compliment fulfills all of the same roles living "
"crew would, all while the ship's systems are auto manned."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30542
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Cleo's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30543
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Auto Salvation"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30544
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30545
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After an encounter with a group of rockmen that almost banished Cleo back to"
" Tartarus, the ex-MFK ghost decided that enough was enough, and thus fully "
"automated his ship, swapping his artillery's boarding drones for combat "
"drones."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30623
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Cleo's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30624
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Ecto-Circuits"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30625
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30626
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_CLEO_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After being stranded in the ruins of a strange, ancient race for weeks, Cleo"
" was amazed to find what seemed to be a pair of pristine AI devices with "
"capabilities far exceeding his own. He also found the blueprints for a "
"scrapped artillery that never went anywhere."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30701
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU\"]/class"
msgstr "Zulu's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30702
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU\"]/name"
msgstr "The Radiance"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30703
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Put to rest the soul of a fanatical Welder to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30704
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"In place of where its life support system should be, Zulu's personal craft "
"instead contains a unique, beam-empowering piece of technology."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30776
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Zulu's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30777
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Mephiles"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30778
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30779
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A twisted reflection of Zulu's cruiser, coming from a universe where the "
"Lanius lost the will to keep fighting for the light."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30854
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Zulu's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30855
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Gamma Ray"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30856
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30857
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_ZULU_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"What radiation is other than very high energy light? Zulu's powers exceeded "
"all expectations, perfecting his healing and his piercing skills. He even "
"recruited some others of himself to his cause."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30930
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G\"]/class"
msgstr "G's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30931
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G\"]/name"
msgstr "The Restitutio"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30932
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Put to rest the soul of a melancholic necromancer to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:30933
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The personal craft of G, a powerful necromancer of Obelisk heritage. The "
"optimizations around the ship have come at the expense of its hull, but its "
"absurdly powerful energy shield renders that a non-issue."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31006
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G_2\"]/class"
msgstr "G's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31007
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Lytikthuk Asath"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31008
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31009
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship is the impossible alliance of all the old empires from the "
"Obelisk's time. Their powers combined are sure to spell the doom of all."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31082
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G_3\"]/class"
msgstr "G's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31083
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Y's Judgement"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31084
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31085
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_G_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser is the result of what could have happened if the Commonwealth's"
" extermination was absolute. A ship unfitting for any crew not deemed "
"'perfect' by Queen Y."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31156
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SPECTER\"]/class"
msgstr "Specter Revenant Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31157
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SPECTER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Soulstone"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31158
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SPECTER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Unlock all non-chaos and non-bonus Revenant ships and their B and C layouts."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31159
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_REVENANT_SPECTER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The cruiser belonging to the maintainers of Tartarus. While not as high up "
"as the Revenants, the Specters make sure every soul's power is properly "
"extracted and made use of."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31232
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL\"]/class"
msgstr "Frostwall's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31233
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL\"]/name"
msgstr "The Frigid Hand"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31234
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Set free the soul of a watchful Sentinel in a chaotic environment to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31235
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser was designed by Frostwall, boasting the most dangerous "
"crystalline hull known. It is designed specifically to take hits as its "
"primary form of offense."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31308
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Frostwall's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31309
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Bloodied Hand"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31310
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31311
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After being shunned from his own faction, Frostwall was forced to lend his "
"skills to the highest bidder. Unfortunately, said highest bidder was the "
"slave clan Tiiikaka."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31385
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Frostwall's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31386
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Faceted Madness"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31387
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31388
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_FROSTWALL_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After fully succumbing to the chaotic madness, Frostwall was fully "
"integrated into the Watcher's ranks, and with that came the installation of "
"the best Rhyme there is."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31465
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM\"]/class"
msgstr "Deathbloom's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31466
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM\"]/name"
msgstr "The Wolfsbane"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31467
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Set free the soul of a diligent Vampweed in a chaotic environment to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31468
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Deathbloom's signature vessel is infested with deadly spores, allowing her "
"and her crew to easily kill any crew standing in their way."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31542
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Deathbloom's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31543
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Aconitine"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31544
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31545
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After reintegrating into Vampweed society, Deathbloom was approached by the "
"Geniocracy and offered a once in a lifetime chance to work with their top "
"scientists. The result? This ungodly ship filled with deadly gas."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31622
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Deathbloom's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31623
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Lifeforce"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31624
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31625
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_DEATHBLOOM_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Intrigued by the efficiency of Deathbloom's spores, a group of Ministry "
"scientists approached her with a novel idea: Combine her spore capabilities "
"with their energy shield technology. This ship is the result."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31702
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK\"]/class"
msgstr "Pok's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31703
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK\"]/name"
msgstr "Tok Kok"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31704
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Set free the soul of a loving Morph in a chaotic environment to unlock this "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31705
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Pok's vessel was likely forged in a similar manner to themselves. The entire"
" ship is alive, which allows it the ability to consume organic matter as "
"sustenance."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31779
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Pok's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31780
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Pork Dork-Tork"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31781
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31782
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This living ship starts with a diverse crew layout, allowing you to feed it "
"all it desires from the start of your journey."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31857
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Pok's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31858
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Mok-Nok"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31859
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31860
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_POK_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After eating so many common aliens over the course of centuries, Pok's ship "
"developed a more... acquired taste. Now all it accepts are extraordinary "
"crew. At least its power absorbing abilities were also heightened."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31933
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR\"]/class"
msgstr "Charror's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31934
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR\"]/name"
msgstr "Segmentation Fault"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31935
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Set free the soul of a broken Defender in a chaotic environment to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:31936
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The personal cruiser of Charror, or Character-Error. Their experimentations "
"with Med-Bots has twisted the nanomachines from their original purpose."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32012
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Charror's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32013
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR_2\"]/name"
msgstr "REPORT ME"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32014
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32015
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR_2\"]/desc"
msgstr "could_not_find: PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR_2: desc"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32092
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Oracle Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32093
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Oracle"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32094
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32095
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_CHARROR_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"No one can remember what universe 50732171 was like. Records of it even "
"within C.E.L. are sparse and frequently go missing. All that's known is that"
" shortly after the Rebel flagship was destroyed, the renegade cruiser "
"collided with an unknown ship. This is the result."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32166
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO\"]/class"
msgstr "Leo's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32167
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO\"]/name"
msgstr "The Quiet Life"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32168
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Set free the soul of a stalwart Ampere in a chaotic environment to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32169
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Leo has configured this ship's engine exhaust in such a way that it can be "
"used as a weapon, draining energy much like the Leeches themselves."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32242
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Leo's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32243
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Quantum Leech"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32244
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32245
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After finding a clan of Augmented Lanius in a secluded sector, Leo decided "
"to offer them a chance to work for him in exchange for their services in "
"upgrading his ship. Their reward? An all you can eat buffet of ships for "
"them to consume."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32321
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Leo's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32322
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Mydoom"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32323
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32324
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_LEO_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Instead of focusing on the ship's engines, Leo decided to put all his scrap "
"into making his ship as intertwined with his hacking system as he could."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32401
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK\"]/class"
msgstr "Searak's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32402
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK\"]/name"
msgstr "Clypeus Fidei"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32403
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Set free the soul of a dogged Martyr in a chaotic environment to unlock this"
" ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32404
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Onboard this vessel, Searak constructed a revolutionary piece of technology "
"that allows his ship to naturally recharge energy shields. Unlike most "
"Duskbringer vessels, it also doesn't even have any support for a clonebay, "
"mostly stemming from Searak's trauma."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32471
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Searak's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32472
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Bright Future"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32473
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32474
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After stopping a rebel plot to blame an attack on the Duskbringer capital on"
" the Federation, Searak, Anurak and Devorak decided to join forces and form "
"their own faction, one unshackled by the sins of their old leaders."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32547
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Searak's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32548
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Ever-Shielded"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32549
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32550
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_SEARAK_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Searak's reintroduction to the Duskbringer cause was the most controversial "
"news since Devorak's speach. With nothing to lose, the once-ex-Duskbringer "
"decided to go all in on explosive tactics."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32625
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO\"]/class"
msgstr "Legionnaire Auto-Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32626
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO\"]/name"
msgstr "Primix"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32627
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Destroy an Auto-ship in the most unlikely location possible in a chaotic "
"environment to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32628
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A prized Rebel vessel which is extremely effective at employing automated "
"defenses without losing the ability to support crew."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32702
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Legionnaire Auto-Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32703
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO_2\"]/name"
msgstr "TemperNet"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32704
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32705
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This modified Legionnaire Auto-Cruiser focuses on both eradicating crew and "
"melting systems without damaging the ship's hull."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32782
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Callie Auto-Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32783
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Callie"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32784
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32785
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUTO_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The Callie The Calculator project was never meant to receive a cruiser, "
"especially not one based off the Legionnaire Auto-Cruiser. The details of "
"why this was made are murky, but one thing that is known for sure is that "
"whoever led this project did so unofficially."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32862
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER\"]/class"
msgstr "Watcher's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32863
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER\"]/name"
msgstr "The Vigilance"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32864
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Destroy an unspeakable abomination in a chaotic environment to unlock this "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32865
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The Watcher's personal cruiser. Pilot this vessel wisely - your new "
"partner's own plans are utterly unknown to everyone except themselves."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32937
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Watcher's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32938
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER_2\"]/name"
msgstr "MKUltra"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32939
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:32940
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"As part of their plan to reform Her, The Watcher required plenty more covert"
" operations to secure assets in important locations. This ship makes use of "
"unique technology to bolster the powers of anyone wearing it while an enemy "
"is mind controlled."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33011
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Watcher's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33012
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Katabasis"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33013
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33014
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_WATCHER_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship is the result of the Watcher being gifted with all but a drop of "
"Her power, giving them her powerful and unique system alongside a set of "
"weapons worthy of her status."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33089
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP\"]/class"
msgstr "Legionnaire Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33090
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP\"]/name"
msgstr "The Turncoat"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33091
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Survive the worst Tartarus has to offer in chaos mode."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33092
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After uncovering the horrible plans that Vance 1 has in store for them, a "
"small collection of legionnaires decided to turn to the Federation in hopes "
"of atoning for their sins. To try and prove their loyalty they also stole "
"Vance 1's prize possession: The Legionnaire Flagship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33167
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Legionnaire Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33168
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Level Of ViolencE"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33169
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33170
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This ship was never sanctioned by the Rebellion. In fact, it was copied by "
"an extremist group within the Legion shortly after they went rogue. There "
"will be no mercy for the crew of this ship, no forgiveness, no survivors."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33244
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/class"
msgstr "'MFK' Flagship"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33245
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Mockery"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33246
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33247
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_LEGION_FLAGSHIP_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After the prototype for his flagship was stolen by Prime's soldiers, Vance 1"
" decided to repaint his own personal flagship to mock their attempt at "
"getting one over him."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33323
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/class"
msgstr "Augustus' Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33324
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/name"
msgstr "Aureum Imperium"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33325
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Put to rest the soul of a greedy Phantom to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33326
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A cruiser wielded by Augustus, the ghost of the richest Phantom to ever "
"live. Its systems contain parts which are supernaturally bolstered, growing "
"in efficiency as more items of value gather around them."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33398
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Augustus' Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33399
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Conversor Argenti"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33400
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33401
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This cruiser has a unique variant of the golden circuits which are made out "
"of pure silver, giving your ship defenses instead of general buffs. It also "
"begins with many resources and no way to use them. Instead, it must convert "
"such resources to scrap first."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33472
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Augustus' Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33473
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Aurum Rosaceum"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33474
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33475
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After years of wandering alone after G's demise, Augustus finally decided to"
" make something of their post-life. Turns out they still have the touch of "
"the trade, with them managing to get in possession of some very rare nebula "
"gasses."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33549
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/class"
msgstr "Sally's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33550
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/name"
msgstr "Nature's Wrath"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33551
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Put to rest the soul of a mad spider to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33552
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After a lot of time spent experimenting, Sally discovered a way to spread "
"spider-kind with little effort: hatch eggs within their enemies, then blow "
"through their bodies and seek life."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33630
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Sally's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33631
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY_2\"]/name"
msgstr "ARC Arachnid"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33632
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33633
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After reconnecting with her old friends, Sally was hired back into the "
"Arcadia's Research Division, with them retrofitting her ship to be up to "
"code with the cooperation's branding."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33709
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Sally's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33710
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY_3\"]/name"
msgstr "Hogna Carolinensis"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33711
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33712
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_SALLY_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After being unable to find support from any faction, Sally turned to the "
"only group that was still willing to treat her like a person. That group "
"was, ironically, the G.A.S.."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33791
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE\"]/class"
msgstr "The Prince's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33792
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE\"]/name"
msgstr "The Nightmare"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33793
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Set free the soul of a demonic Equinoid in a chaotic environment to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33794
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Enemies can't even really fight back against the Prince's personal craft, "
"allowing it to slowly pick their crew apart one by one."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33871
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE_2\"]/class"
msgstr "The Prince's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33872
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE_2\"]/name"
msgstr "Lelth Yl' F'sol"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33873
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33874
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"After attempting to disrupt the plans of the Messengers, the Prince of Darkness was unexpectedly captured and enslaved by the very same group he was attempting to take down. \n"
"As payback, the Messengers took over his cruiser and retrofitted it with their colors."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33948
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE_3\"]/class"
msgstr "The Prince's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33949
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Pact"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33950
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:33951
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_PRINCE_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The Prince of Darkness once ruled over the upper layers of Hell with their "
"specialty being forming pacts with desperate souls, something they stopped "
"doing once summoned into reality. This ship is their return to form."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34024
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC\"]/class"
msgstr "Tririac's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34025
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC\"]/name"
msgstr "The Truth"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34026
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Set free the soul of a blasphemic Thing in a chaotic environment to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34027
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Tririac and their allies have discovered a number of secrets that She and "
"The One Who Rhymes have been hiding from him. Now, all they care about is "
"exposing the gods, in a ship constructed out of blasphemy made manifest."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34100
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC_2\"]/class"
msgstr "Tririac's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34101
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC_2\"]/name"
msgstr "The Dilation"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34102
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC_2\"]/unlock"
msgstr "Get to Sector 5 with the Type A to unlock this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34103
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"They say to be able to beat one's enemy, you must learn all you can about "
"their abilities. Tririac seem to have taken this to their non-existent "
"heart, as they achieved something akin to mastery over the temporal system's"
" time slowing abilities."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34177
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC_3\"]/class"
msgstr "Tririac's Cruiser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34178
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC_3\"]/name"
msgstr "The Trance"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34179
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC_3\"]/unlock"
msgstr ""
"Get to Sector 5 with the Type B or beat the game with the Type A to unlock "
"this ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:34180
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//shipBlueprint[@name=\"PLAYER_SHIP_FR_BONUS_REVENANT_TRIRIAC_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"They say the enemy of your enemy is your friend. Tririac, having run out of "
"options for support, had to ally himself with the Utopians in hopes of "
"eventually being able to take Her down for good."
